<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Liam James — CV</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .page {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
            min-height: 297mm;
        }

        /* ---- Sidebar ---- */
        .sidebar {
            background: #1e2a3a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .sidebar-photo {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center top;
            display: block;
        }

        .sidebar-content {
            padding: 24px 20px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .sidebar h3 {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .sidebar-section {
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .sidebar-section p,
        .sidebar-section li {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #c8d0da;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .sidebar-section ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .sidebar-section ul li {
            padding-left: 14px;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sidebar-section ul li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 8px;
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #7b8da0;
        }

        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #c8d0da;
        }

        .contact-item span.icon {
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        .edu-entry {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .edu-entry .edu-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }

        .edu-entry .edu-school {
            font-size: 8.5pt;
            color: #9aa8b8;
        }

        .sidebar-location {
            margin-top: auto;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #9aa8b8;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        /* ---- Testimonial ---- */
        .testimonial {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-left: 3px solid #7b8da0;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }

        .testimonial p {
            font-size: 8.5pt;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #c8d0da;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .testimonial .testimonial-author {
            font-size: 8pt;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .testimonial .testimonial-role {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            font-style: normal;
            color: #9aa8b8;
        }

        /* ---- Main Content ---- */
        .main {
            padding: 36px 32px;
        }

        .main-header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-header h1 {
            font-size: 26pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .main-header h2 {
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #5a6a7a;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .summary {
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #3a3a3a;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            max-width: 520px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1e2a3a;
        }

        /* ---- Job Entry ---- */
        .job {
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .job-header {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .job-company {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .job-company-desc {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6a7a8a;
        }

        .job-role {
            font-size: 10pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2a3a4a;
        }

        .job-date {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #7a8a9a;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .job ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .job ul li {
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #3a3a3a;
            padding-left: 14px;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .job ul li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 8px;
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #1e2a3a;
        }

        .references {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #7a8a9a;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* ---- Print ---- */
        @media print {
            body { background: #fff; }
            .page {
                width: 210mm;
                min-height: 297mm;
                margin: 0;
            }
        }

        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page">
    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <img src="/assets/headshot.jpeg" alt="Liam James" class="sidebar-photo">
        <div class="sidebar-content">

            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h3>Contact</h3>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <span class="icon">+371 27839471</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <span>info@liam-james.uk</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <span>linkedin.com/in/ljak</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <span>liam-james.uk</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <span>Latvia, UK, Remote</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h3>Skills</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Sales leadership</li>
                    <li>GTM strategy & execution</li>
                    <li>Sales enablement</li>
                    <li>Partnership development</li>
                    <li>Lead generation</li>
                    <li>Negotiation & closing</li>
                    <li>Forecasting</li>
                    <li>Team coaching</li>
                    <li>Strategic planning</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h3>Education</h3>
                <div class="edu-entry">
                    <p class="edu-title">BSc, Police & Criminal Investigation</p>
                    <p class="edu-school">University of Central Lancashire | 2012 &ndash; 2015</p>
                </div>
                <div class="edu-entry">
                    <p class="edu-title">BTEC Diploma, Public Services</p>
                    <p class="edu-school">Aylesbury College | 2010 &ndash; 2012</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Force Management</li>
                    <li>Salesforce</li>
                    <li>Slack</li>
                    <li>GitHub</li>
                    <li>Jira & Confluence</li>
                    <li>Google Workspace</li>
                    <li>Microsoft Office</li>
                    <li>Zoom & Teams</li>
                    <li>CRM & enablement tools</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"As an Account Executive, Liam's performance was nothing short of exceptional. He consistently exceeded quotas and quickly became the top-performing sales representative at Lokalise."</p>
                <span class="testimonial-author">Niklas Hisginer</span><br>
                <span class="testimonial-role">CS Manager, Lokalise</span>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"As a manager, Liam always stood up for his team and made sure that we're equipped with the right skills, mindset and tools to perform our best."</p>
                <span class="testimonial-author">Ismails Ahmed</span><br>
                <span class="testimonial-role">Senior AE, ChartMogul</span>
            </div>

        </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Main -->
    <main class="main">
        <div class="main-header">
            <h1>Liam James</h1>
            <h2>Sales & GTM Leader</h2>
        </div>

        <p class="summary">English by birth, Latvian by choice. Most of my career has been spent at the sharp end of revenue: building sales teams, designing enablement programmes, and figuring out what actually makes deals close. At Lokalise, I played a key role in scaling ARR from &euro;1M to &euro;30M, contributing approximately &euro;7M in direct revenue across five years and four roles. Today I build sales systems and GTM strategies so startups can turn early traction into repeatable revenue.</p>

        <h3 class="section-title">Work Experience</h3>

        <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
                <span class="job-company">tem energy</span>
                <span class="job-company-desc"> &mdash; Remote | AI-Powered Energy Platform</span>
            </div>
            <p class="job-role">Sales & Partnerships Manager</p>
            <p class="job-date">Sep 2025 &ndash; Mar 2026</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Led sales and partnership growth, driving pipeline development and market expansion.</li>
                <li>Built scalable GTM systems with repeatable sales processes and partnership programmes.</li>
                <li>Coached the commercial team on strategic, consultative selling.</li>
                <li>Partnered cross-functionally with Product, Marketing, and Design.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
                <span class="job-company">Lokalise</span>
                <span class="job-company-desc"> &mdash; Remote | SaaS Localization Platform</span>
            </div>

            <p class="job-role">Sales Enablement Lead</p>
            <p class="job-date">Jan 2025 &ndash; Aug 2025</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Designed and implemented onboarding and continuous sales training programmes.</li>
                <li>Developed sales collateral and tools to improve rep performance and deal velocity.</li>
                <li>Aligned enablement initiatives with strategic sales goals, collaborating across Product, Marketing, and Sales Ops.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="job-role" style="margin-top: 14px;">Sales Manager</p>
            <p class="job-date">Nov 2023 &ndash; Feb 2025</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Recruited, trained, and led a team of sales reps, managing performance and KPIs.</li>
                <li>Executed sales strategies aligned to revenue goals and forecasted accurately to leadership.</li>
                <li>Drove cross-functional initiatives to improve customer journey and sales effectiveness.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="job-role" style="margin-top: 14px;">Account Executive Team Lead</p>
            <p class="job-date">Mar 2023 &ndash; Nov 2023</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Led a high-performing AE team; exceeded target at 120% attainment.</li>
                <li>Managed strategic enterprise deals from discovery through close.</li>
                <li>Acted as bridge between reps and leadership, feeding market insight into GTM planning.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="job-role" style="margin-top: 14px;">Senior Account Executive</p>
            <p class="job-date">Jul 2022 &ndash; Mar 2023</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Delivered 110&ndash;120% quota attainment across two quarters.</li>
                <li>Closed high-value enterprise deals; mentored junior AEs.</li>
                <li>Provided market feedback to influence product development and GTM alignment.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="job-role" style="margin-top: 14px;">Account Executive</p>
            <p class="job-date">Feb 2020 &ndash; Jul 2022</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Prospected and closed deals with high-fit accounts; 2021 performance at 160%.</li>
                <li>Ran end-to-end sales cycles including demo, negotiation, and onboarding.</li>
                <li>Managed pipeline and account growth with strong customer retention.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
                <span class="job-company">Sales & Business Coach</span>
                <span class="job-company-desc"> &mdash; Riga, Latvia (Self-employed)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="job-date">Apr 2018 &ndash; Feb 2020</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Trained early-stage businesses on lead generation, value-selling, and deal closing.</li>
                <li>Delivered 1:1 coaching to founders and SDRs on sales process optimisation.</li>
                <li>Designed early-stage tech stack workflows.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="references">References available on request.</p>

    </main>
</div>

</body>
</html>
